{"tid":1883143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太古城武肺患者 到過西灣河","createTime":"2020-02-16T17:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T02:35:05.000Z","uid":95138,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7a33ea89ca4dc751081fe194fe734a813901ae50","tid":1883143,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"而患者發病後，2月9日曾到過西灣河富欣閣1字樓的樓上教會、「基督門徒福音會西灣河分會」參與聚會，衞生署稱正了解有幾多人屬接觸者需追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n又係西灣河<br />\n之前已經有5單同西灣河有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cfa2eda86ebce2b3ddc2622febb3e7255114f3","tid":1883143,"uid":95138,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:35:51.000Z","msg":"他於2月7日起發燒，同日及2月10日、13日及15日均有向太古城的高志輝醫生求醫，不過於2月10日及15日，因得知他發燒，私家醫生建議病人至東區醫院急症室求診。<br />\n<br />\n2月7至2月15期間可能曾經喺太古城播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26f703608e3eebdc2bc54f95478c6fc3ea96fa0","tid":1883143,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:36:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abec332dc696fbbd73434fe28f01b855f3d98ccb","tid":1883143,"uid":23672,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:38:52.000Z","msg":"西灣河真係好撚高危"},{"pid":"f9f91c8fa6e2c27bea14c177cc69b507165a7416","tid":1883143,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"太安樓個單上面已經有巴打fc咗<br />\n證實太安樓=長興大廈第38號患者<br />\n而38號患者嘅屋企人尋日亦都確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以而家西灣河總共係五個確診個案：23，38，39，40 + 個案16 曾經到過西灣河教堂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，有幾位巴絲都指出<span style=\"color: red;\">成安街街市</span>衛生環境惡劣，而且恐怕有大陸湖北嘅員工，屬高危環境，請大家小心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z58